1
00:00:36,180 --> 00:00:40,940
=Ancient Bracelet=

2
00:00:41,340 --> 00:00:44,380
=Episode 9=

3
00:00:44,420 --> 00:00:46,660
=Do You Have Feelings for Me?=

4
00:00:47,670 --> 00:00:48,510
Zhaoli.

5
00:00:56,000 --> 00:00:57,320
From now on, do not leave

6
00:00:57,640 --> 00:00:59,470
without telling me.

7
00:01:20,350 --> 00:01:22,710
(If I don't keep an eye on her
for a day,)

8
00:01:22,750 --> 00:01:24,370
(she starts thinking
about another man.)

9
00:01:29,150 --> 00:01:29,990
Zhaoli,

10
00:01:31,790 --> 00:01:32,630
wake up.

11
00:01:33,310 --> 00:01:35,150
Don't leave me behind.

12
00:01:37,430 --> 00:01:39,350
Now, I just want to throw you out.

13
00:01:47,000 --> 00:01:47,840
Ying Du?

14
00:01:48,400 --> 00:01:49,510
You're back.

15
00:01:52,070 --> 00:01:53,790
Why are you hauling me around?

16
00:01:55,560 --> 00:01:58,200
You're ruining my sweet dream.

17
00:01:58,200 --> 00:01:59,040
Sweet dream?

18
00:01:59,920 --> 00:02:01,400
Were you dreaming about Yan Che again?

19
00:02:02,040 --> 00:02:03,150
Of course not.

20
00:02:05,870 --> 00:02:08,030
Is it the one from your previous dreams?

21
00:02:09,870 --> 00:02:10,710
Then did you

22
00:02:16,590 --> 00:02:17,710
dream of me?

23
00:02:23,400 --> 00:02:24,870
Zhaoli, do you have feelings

24
00:02:24,870 --> 00:02:25,710
for me?

25
00:02:28,390 --> 00:02:32,400
♪Your gaze blooms with grace♪

26
00:02:33,800 --> 00:02:35,410
♪Affection fills the air♪

27
00:02:35,960 --> 00:02:37,190
Is this real?

28
00:02:38,910 --> 00:02:39,800
You don't like it?

29
00:02:40,750 --> 00:02:42,120
Then I'll take it back.

30
00:02:43,190 --> 00:02:45,380
♪Your love♪

31
00:02:45,380 --> 00:02:48,280
♪Like warm winds drifting through♪

32
00:02:49,840 --> 00:02:50,680
Zhaoli,

33
00:02:51,680 --> 00:02:52,520
thank you.

34
00:02:53,800 --> 00:02:57,120
♪Flowers fall and bloom
without a script♪

35
00:02:59,800 --> 00:03:00,640
Your hand...

36
00:03:02,360 --> 00:03:03,200
It's fine.

37
00:03:03,560 --> 00:03:04,400
Don't worry.

38
00:03:08,826 --> 00:03:10,040
The Frostbite Curse in Ying Du

39
00:03:10,051 --> 00:03:11,590
has been striking more often.

40
00:03:11,960 --> 00:03:14,360
Could it be from losing his power?

41
00:03:18,560 --> 00:03:19,400
Oracle.

42
00:03:19,590 --> 00:03:21,630
(Oracle)
A century-old herb for you.

43
00:03:22,560 --> 00:03:24,000
Do you know how to break

44
00:03:24,000 --> 00:03:25,960
the backlash from losing one's power?

45
00:03:26,560 --> 00:03:29,400
Why do people keep asking me this?

46
00:03:34,430 --> 00:03:35,750
I don't know the cure

47
00:03:36,030 --> 00:03:38,470
for that kind of backlash either.

48
00:03:38,680 --> 00:03:40,120
But there is one way

49
00:03:40,120 --> 00:03:41,960
to sever one's sense of pain.

50
00:03:41,960 --> 00:03:43,590
Once the pain is gone,

51
00:03:43,680 --> 00:03:45,190
the harm one takes

52
00:03:45,360 --> 00:03:46,630
will lessen as well.

53
00:03:47,590 --> 00:03:48,470
What method is that?

54
00:03:48,870 --> 00:03:50,400
The Soulfall Ring.

55
00:03:50,630 --> 00:03:53,120
- But its whereabouts are unknown.
- The Soulfall Ring.

56
00:03:53,120 --> 00:03:54,710
It's not easy to find.

57
00:03:56,240 --> 00:03:57,110
Still,

58
00:03:57,120 --> 00:03:58,680
I can't just take this herb

59
00:03:59,030 --> 00:04:01,000
for nothing.

60
00:04:01,680 --> 00:04:04,630
You've been looking radiant lately.

61
00:04:05,360 --> 00:04:08,240
Have you found someone you like?

62
00:04:12,190 --> 00:04:13,030
But

63
00:04:13,360 --> 00:04:14,430
you two are trapped

64
00:04:14,710 --> 00:04:17,950
in a cycle of grudges and tangled fate.

65
00:04:18,000 --> 00:04:19,480
If you keep holding on,

66
00:04:19,630 --> 00:04:22,680
you'll lose everyone you hold dear.

67
00:04:22,680 --> 00:04:24,510
You and he are destined

68
00:04:24,510 --> 00:04:26,950
to meet as enemies, bound by hate.

69
00:04:36,160 --> 00:04:38,240
Though I dislike Oracle's words,

70
00:04:39,480 --> 00:04:41,720
he's the heaven-eyed diviner.

71
00:04:43,040 --> 00:04:44,480
The fortunes he casts

72
00:04:46,630 --> 00:04:48,510
have never been wrong.

73
00:04:49,870 --> 00:04:50,710
Be careful.

74
00:05:22,920 --> 00:05:23,760
Che.

75
00:05:25,140 --> 00:05:26,000
Zhaoli,

76
00:05:26,000 --> 00:05:26,840
it's me.

77
00:05:30,523 --> 00:05:32,236
Zhaoli said she'd come
to the Ghost Market.

78
00:05:32,390 --> 00:05:33,390
Why don't I see her?

79
00:05:40,160 --> 00:05:42,040
Zhaoli, let's talk somewhere else.

80
00:05:43,120 --> 00:05:43,960
Come.

81
00:05:45,270 --> 00:05:46,110
(Yan Che?)

82
00:05:46,680 --> 00:05:48,190
(How does he know my spells?)

83
00:05:48,630 --> 00:05:50,240
(Could he be the man in black?)

84
00:05:53,190 --> 00:05:54,030
Your Majesty,

85
00:05:54,487 --> 00:05:55,327
I've found something.

86
00:05:55,338 --> 00:05:57,506
Lately, a mysterious figure
skilled in spells appeared

87
00:05:57,517 --> 00:05:58,661
by the Grand Princess's side.

88
00:05:58,672 --> 00:06:00,622
That man is Yan Che of the Wuyue tribe.

89
00:06:04,160 --> 00:06:05,510
He hides himself well.

90
00:06:05,870 --> 00:06:07,270
What is he really after?

91
00:06:08,390 --> 00:06:09,230
Zhaoli.

92
00:06:14,360 --> 00:06:15,200
Che,

93
00:06:15,750 --> 00:06:17,560
when did you learn spells?

94
00:06:17,680 --> 00:06:19,000
They're exactly like Ying Du's.

95
00:06:19,680 --> 00:06:21,270
I learned them while cultivating.

96
00:06:23,870 --> 00:06:25,870
What were you about to tell me just now?

97
00:06:26,040 --> 00:06:26,880
Zhaoli,

98
00:06:27,550 --> 00:06:28,570
I feel that there's a bond

99
00:06:28,581 --> 00:06:29,870
by nature between us.

100
00:06:30,360 --> 00:06:31,510
I often have the same dream.

101
00:06:33,510 --> 00:06:34,390
In my dream,

102
00:06:34,760 --> 00:06:35,620
we've shared

103
00:06:35,630 --> 00:06:36,950
countless nights as a couple.

104
00:06:39,700 --> 00:06:40,550
A dream?

105
00:06:40,560 --> 00:06:41,973
These past years, I've kept dreaming

106
00:06:41,984 --> 00:06:43,040
we're inside a palace

107
00:06:43,446 --> 00:06:45,160
when suddenly,
the man in black bursts in.

108
00:06:45,200 --> 00:06:46,070
In that dream,

109
00:06:46,070 --> 00:06:47,789
I managed to block his attack
just in time.

110
00:06:53,190 --> 00:06:54,040
Your dream

111
00:06:54,720 --> 00:06:56,360
is exactly the same as mine.

112
00:06:56,360 --> 00:06:57,920
Oracle says it's a foretelling dream.

113
00:06:58,160 --> 00:06:59,690
Zhaoli, I'm worried about you.

114
00:07:00,040 --> 00:07:02,310
But why speak of it only now?

115
00:07:02,800 --> 00:07:03,950
I never mentioned it before,

116
00:07:04,560 --> 00:07:05,410
because I believed

117
00:07:05,410 --> 00:07:07,120
we'd naturally end up together.

118
00:07:07,680 --> 00:07:09,190
But since Ying Du arrived,

119
00:07:09,190 --> 00:07:10,680
he's all you think about.

120
00:07:11,480 --> 00:07:12,830
I wanted to let go,

121
00:07:14,070 --> 00:07:15,630
but I couldn't.

122
00:07:16,630 --> 00:07:17,470
Zhaoli,

123
00:07:18,800 --> 00:07:20,390
will you give me one more chance?

124
00:07:23,560 --> 00:07:24,400
Yes.

125
00:07:24,560 --> 00:07:26,040
I used to be so fixated

126
00:07:26,040 --> 00:07:27,800
on finding the one from my dream.

127
00:07:28,270 --> 00:07:30,680
Because I thought it was
a foretelling dream.

128
00:07:31,480 --> 00:07:33,430
But ever since Ying Du appeared,

129
00:07:34,430 --> 00:07:36,360
I haven't had that dream again.

130
00:07:39,000 --> 00:07:40,560
Perhaps my worry was needless.

131
00:07:42,310 --> 00:07:43,036
Zhaoli,

132
00:07:43,047 --> 00:07:44,525
this is a rare treasure I came across

133
00:07:44,536 --> 00:07:45,480
during my cultivation.

134
00:07:45,830 --> 00:07:47,310
They say it can block out pain.

135
00:07:47,310 --> 00:07:48,360
I want you to have it.

136
00:07:48,430 --> 00:07:49,510
May it keep you safe.

137
00:07:49,920 --> 00:07:51,120
The Soulfall Ring.

138
00:07:51,920 --> 00:07:53,560
You recognize it?

139
00:07:53,673 --> 00:07:54,593
(Only this can soothe)

140
00:07:54,604 --> 00:07:56,720
(the agony Ying Du suffers
from the Frostbite Curse.)

141
00:07:57,360 --> 00:07:58,220
Che,

142
00:07:58,270 --> 00:07:59,360
I'll take this then.

143
00:07:59,910 --> 00:08:00,750
Thank you.

144
00:08:00,870 --> 00:08:02,720
I thought you'd refuse it.

145
00:08:03,600 --> 00:08:05,480
This treasure is far too precious.

146
00:08:05,920 --> 00:08:07,510
I'll give you all the money

147
00:08:07,680 --> 00:08:09,070
and rare herbs

148
00:08:09,310 --> 00:08:10,270
I've saved up

149
00:08:10,430 --> 00:08:11,270
to exchange for it.

150
00:08:11,270 --> 00:08:12,583
I'll fetch them for you right now.

151
00:08:13,390 --> 00:08:14,430
I don't want your money.

152
00:08:16,600 --> 00:08:17,440
This alone is enough.

153
00:08:24,300 --> 00:08:25,430
Ying Du, what are you doing?

154
00:08:25,430 --> 00:08:26,393
Don't speak up for him.

155
00:08:26,433 --> 00:08:27,510
But acting like this...

156
00:08:29,720 --> 00:08:30,560
Zhaoli.

157
00:08:42,750 --> 00:08:44,720
I won't allow you to treat her this way.

158
00:08:47,750 --> 00:08:49,080
What are you trying to do?

159
00:08:49,720 --> 00:08:51,150
So what if you won't allow it?

160
00:08:54,120 --> 00:08:55,120
Yan Che.

161
00:09:02,580 --> 00:09:07,230
♪Snow falls upon my brows,
blurring suddenly♪

162
00:09:09,060 --> 00:09:14,030
♪Memories turn,
forgiving time after time♪

163
00:09:15,490 --> 00:09:18,770
♪Tears or snowflakes, sweet or bitter♪

164
00:09:18,770 --> 00:09:21,670
♪Hard to tell them apart♪

165
00:09:22,190 --> 00:09:27,480
♪Vowing to give you
three lifetimes' happiness♪

166
00:09:27,480 --> 00:09:31,180
♪In this life, I still run toward you♪

167
00:09:31,530 --> 00:09:33,880
♪No matter the homeward journey♪

168
00:09:33,880 --> 00:09:37,920
♪Falling to the deepest place
in your heart♪

169
00:09:37,920 --> 00:09:40,300
♪And that is enough♪

170
00:09:40,300 --> 00:09:44,090
♪Ahead lies a path without snow or wind♪

171
00:09:44,300 --> 00:09:47,060
♪Begonia blooms across the branches♪

172
00:09:47,430 --> 00:09:53,180
♪One more glance
may let love stand still♪

173
